  <div class="panel-body">
    <ol>
                <li class="odd">Spread butter on backside of bread and then place on stove (or alternative method of heating).</li>
                <br>
                
                <li class="even">Place preferred cheese on slice of bread, along with bacon.</li>
                <br>
                
                <li class="odd">Wait for cheese to melt and wait for bread to get as toasted as desired.</li>
